        "summary": "POST /api/gl/revrec/contracts",
        "description": "Creates a revenue contract with performance obligations.\nAtomic: contract + obligations + outbox event in a single transaction.\nIdempotent: returns 409 CONFLICT if contract_id already exists.",
        "operationId": "create_contract",
